scene.message:
Mai: Aaah!!{nl}
Mr. Bear!{nl}
Mr. Bear died!{waitkey}{clearbox}Waaaaaah!{nl}
Nobody is nice{nl}
to little Mai!{waitkey}Be nicer to me!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: She vanished...{nl}
Somehow... I feel like{nl}
we did a bad thing...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Honestly...{nl}
This is what comes of Inaba{nl}
scaring her like that!{waitkey}We've lost a valuable{nl}
source of information.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: That bear...{nl}
was her only friend.{nl}
And we...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: A real little witch,{nl}
all right. That was close.{nl}
Still...{waitkey}felt kinda bad for her.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ugh!{nl}
It's 'cause Inaba said{nl}
something he shouldn't!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: What was I supposed{nl}
to do! I never figured{nl}
it'd turn out like this...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I see...{nl}
She must've dropped it.{nl}
Leaves a bad taste, but{waitkey}let's borrow it.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: It grants any wish,{nl}
right...? Should we have{nl}
it carry us to the castle?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: All right.{nl}
It went something like this.{nl}
Nomoraka tanomama!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: No such easy luck.{nl}
Likely only that child{nl}
can use it.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1},{nl}
show me that compact.{waitkey}{clearbox}Huh, it's only half, but{nl}
it's the same as mine...{waitkey}Mine has no mirror, but{nl}
this one has it set{nl}
in properly.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Well, wishes are{nl}
something you grant{nl}
yourself, after all.{waitkey}If everything went your{nl}
way, the world'd be{nl}
boring, wouldn't it.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Kandori...{nl}
what does he mean to do{nl}
once he has that compact...?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I remember when I was{nl}
small, I'd pretend our mirror{nl}
at home was a magic one{waitkey}and make wishes to it.{waitkey}{clearbox}'Let me become a pretty girl{nl}
everyone likes,'{nl}
or something like that...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Aw~ such a shame.{nl}
I've got so many wishes,{nl}
too.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ohh, and I've got so{nl}
many things I want!{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, buy them for me?{waitkey}{ret}
